@node Main "Permutax - Documentation"

                             'Permutax' 1.2

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Permutax' is a Workbench @{" game " link play} where you try to clear 25 boards
filled with various coloured tiles, the idea is to permutate 2 tiles
in such a way that at least one tile match 1 to 4 neighbouring tiles
(either on the left, right, upper row or lower row). When neighbouring
tiles match, they are removed from the board.

  An important advice: just don't isolate lone tiles!

  Have fun!

